IN RE: T.T.E. 238A18-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 6, 2019

Michelle F. Lynch, Attorney at Law, For T.T.E.

Janelle E. Varley, Assistant Attorney General, Todd Williams, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 4th of March 2019 by Juvenile-Appellee to Withdraw as Private Assigned Counsel and to Appoint the Appellate Defender:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th of March 2019."
